      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. that's a good start. i feel like i could definitely work with those.\n\ni was also thinking about how these tropes aren't just limited to one group. a lot of times movies use similar types of caricatures for latinos or asiatic characters too, just different \"flavors\" of the same thing. do you have any examples for those groups? it would help me make sure my satire covers the whole industry and doesnt feel like it's only targeting one thing.",
